################################################################################
# Github & GitLab Rpos.
#   Many uses individual keys. But some share the SSH 
#   keys. Since Github requires primary emails to be unique as alternative uids,
#   the email is aliased to pilakkat+<repo-name>@gmail.com. This allows multiple 
#   accounts to share the same email address, while still being able to use 
#   different SSH keys for each account.
 ################################################################################
#
#

